			<title>Web-Savvy Accessibility Challenge Page</title>
			<link>https://legacy.idrc.ocadu.ca/resources/idrc-online/23-conference-slides/291-web-savvy-accessibility-challenge-page</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://legacy.idrc.ocadu.ca/resources/idrc-online/23-conference-slides/291-web-savvy-accessibility-challenge-page</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<h1>Help! I\'m a page with problems. </h1>  <p>If you use me with adaptive technology, this is what is likely to happen:</p>  <img border="0" src="http://snow.utoronto.ca/access/higher/crash.gif" /> <p>  <table cellpadding="15" border="0" bgcolor="#339966"><tbody><tr><td>Some people who are colour blind have problems with certain combinations for background and font colours. </td></tr></tbody></table>  </p><hr /> <h1>Had enough?? Fix the problems, and ensure that you are reaching the widest possible audience! </h1>]]></description>
